ent management <strong>system Contao is divided</strong> into two areas: the back end (administration area) and the front end (website). If you are reading this you are currently viewing the front end. To log in to the back end, simply add <em>/contao</em> to the URL of the site (https://demo.contao.org/contao).</p>', NULL, '', '', '', NULL, '', 'above', NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 'ascending', '', '', '', '', 'sourceText', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', NULL, 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', NULL, '', '', NULL, '', NULL, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, 0, 300, 0, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', '', 'ascending', 0, '', 'col-4 col-4-md col-4-lg offset-left-0 offset-left-0-md offset-left-0-lg offset-right-0 offset-right-0-md offset-right-0-lg', '', '', 'left', 'right', 1, 0, 0, '');
